'''奥托克罗姆'''（{{lang-fr|Autochrome}}），也称为“天然彩色像片技术”。是一种早期的彩色摄影的技术。1903年由法国的[[卢米埃兄弟|卢米埃兄弟]]获得专利，并于1907年投入市场。在20世纪30年代中期的[[減色法|減色法]]發明之前，奥托克罗姆是主要的摄影方法<ref>French patent 339,223, Dec. 17, 1903. [http://books.google.com/books?id=wyAAAAAAMAAJ&q=lumiere+339,223&dq=lumiere+339,223&lr=&as_brr=0&ei=3VqlR6agHpnmiQGMi6WnCg&pgis=1  ''Journal of the Society of Chemical Industry,''] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=wyAAAAAAMAAJ&q=lumiere+339,223&dq=lumiere+339,223&lr=&as_brr=0&ei=3VqlR6agHpnmiQGMi6WnCg&pgis=1 |date=20121114093808 }} 1905.</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = The Encyclopædia Britannica: A Dictionary of Arts, Sciences, Literature and General Information | author = Hugh Chisholm | edition = 11th | year = 1911 | pages = XXI.501 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=xe8tAAAAIAAJ&pg=RA2-PA501&dq=Autochrome+Lumi%C3%A8re+orange+green+violet+1907 | nopp = true | publisher = The Encyclopædia Britannica Company }}</ref>。

奥托克罗姆是第一个成功进行商业化的彩色摄影技术。

